No wonder we are lagging behind especially with our children.It is for that reason that recently I came across a member of this ‘Fab Four Authority’,one Agness Penya Renedo.

While saying all these things, I have never met her but I come across her teaching that I vividly remember saying “It takes courage to act” and than I said it repeatedly until I found out that she is one of the founders of this company called Fab Four Authority.

I followed her on Twitter and I realised there is more she can teach us than just be creative.

I am informed that she can teach online entrepreneurs to eliminate stress,choose the right tools to manage their social media accounts,how to convert their Twitter and Facebook fans into loyal customers and clients,entially generate more revenue.

What more purposes does she have? Oh I forgot, she’s creative and she can help your sales by hosting live online selling events & talks on how to enhance your content, best ways to monetize your audience and more techniques to turn social media fans into paying subscribers,effectively build a successful online business without the help of a famous promoter.

With all these claims in place, you and I can either take her as a snake so it doesn’t bite or she is just one of those people who are seeing the clouds and are not navigating to reach there.
